title: 4 Rare 80s Albums [Part 163] New Wave, Synth, Post-Punk
description:
Here's another 4 obscure but equally awesome records from underground end of music, the un-loved and unknown bands of the new wave era. Another sample of cast off rejects of our musical culture that made all the innovations and inroads and new kinds of music but got none of the glory or the money!


A Day In Paris - Prey [1988]

Mission - The Last Detail [1983]

No More - Laughter in the Wings [1985]

The Chyldren - Mortis Hora [1987]
